<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title>Verify Your Email - MVLLI</title>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
				background-color: #f5f5f5;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
				color: #1a1a1a;
			}
			.container {
				max-width: 600px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				background: white;
				border-radius: 16px;
				padding: 40px;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(45, 74, 43, 0.1);
				border: 1px solid rgba(45, 74, 43, 0.1);
			}
			.header {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 30px;
			}
			.logo {
				font-size: 2rem;
				font-weight: 800;
				color: #2d4a2b;
				margin-bottom: 10px;
				font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
			}
			.welcome-text {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				color: #666;
				margin-bottom: 30px;
			}
			.verify-button {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 14px 32px;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d4a2b 0%, #3a5a40 100%);
				color: white;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 12px;
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 1rem;
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(45, 74, 43, 0.3);
			}
			.verify-button:hover {
				transform: translateY(-2px);
				box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(45, 74, 43, 0.4);
			}
			.link-text {
				margin-top: 20px;
				padding: 15px;
				background: rgba(45, 74, 43, 0.05);
				border-radius: 8px;
				word-break: break-all;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
			}
			.footer {
				margin-top: 30px;
				padding-top: 20px;
				border-top: 1px solid rgba(45, 74, 43, 0.1);
				text-align: center;
				color: #666;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="header">
				<div class="logo">MVLLI</div>
				<div class="welcome-text">Welcome {{ user.name|default(user.username) }}!</div>
			</div>

			<p>Thank you for registering with MVLLI. Please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>

			<p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
				<a href="{{ verificationUrl }}" class="verify-button">
					Verify Email Address
				</a>
			</p>

			<p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
			<div class="link-text">{{ verificationUrl }}</div>

			<p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">If you did not create an account, please ignore this email.</p>

			<div class="footer">
				<p>Thanks,<br>The MVLLI Team</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>